  "title": "💎 [ENTRY LVL] Events Sales Crew | Face-to-Face | Training Provided | Travel Opportunities 💎",
  "description": "<p><strong>Entry-Level Events Sales | No Experience Needed</strong></p><p>Looking for a job that isn’t stuck behind a desk? Want to meet new people, learn useful skills, and work with a fun, supportive team?</p><p>If you’re open to learning, enjoy talking to people, and want a role where you can grow while earning — this could be a great fit for you.</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p>🤝 Chat with customers face-to-face at events and roadshows</p><p>🗣 Represent brands in a friendly, confident way</p><p>📈 Learn sales and communication skills on the job</p><p>👯‍♂️ Work closely with teammates during live events</p><p><br /><strong>What You’ll Get</strong></p><p>🎓 No experience needed — full training from day one</p><p>🤝 One-to-one guidance and daily support</p><p>💰 Weekly payouts + incentives</p><p>✈️ Opportunities to travel locally and overseas</p><p>⚖️ Supportive team culture with good work-life balance</p><p>📊 Clear growth opportunities if you want to level up</p><p><br /><strong>Who This Is For</strong></p><p>🌱 Positive, open-minded individuals</p><p>🗣 Comfortable talking to people (or willing to learn)</p><p>🤝 Team players who want to grow together</p><p><br />Fresh grads, students, and career switchers are welcome.</p><p>📩 <strong>Interested?</strong> Apply now and let’s grow together 🚀<br /></p><p>Shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
